{"tid":2029911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[527行動] 可唔可以各區 不要圍立法會? 次次港島都係最低效","createTime":"2020-05-22T13:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T13:21:33.000Z","uid":102787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41888e5c1f5696d07d9fe5791b8a516a1ac14639","tid":2029911,"uid":102787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">For 嫌長唔想睇 -&gt; 各區示威永遠比集中一區既影響大</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行動一定要有, 但圍立法會如同圍狗總<br />\n覺得今次會好似612比你聚大半日人?<br />\n留守到第2日 又聚得到?<br />\n點解要去最重狗既地方？<br />\n警總咁撚大 可以聚集更多裝備同狗隻<br />\n狗總&lt;&gt;立法會 6分鐘車程, 行過黎仲快</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03nwngK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03nwngK.png&h=ace787e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫講話929 大意比速龍係政總出黎拉撚左 100+人<br />\n<img src=\"https://archive.org/download/Hong-Kong-Protests-2019-09-29-e44b9307635adb69ef2902033172eb8e1f24bbf2/Hong-Kong-Protests-2019-09-29-e44b9307635adb69ef2902033172eb8e1f24bbf2.thumbs/速龍政總偷襲_000005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdownload%2FHong-Kong-Protests-2019-09-29-e44b9307635adb69ef2902033172eb8e1f24bbf2%2FHong-Kong-Protests-2019-09-29-e44b9307635adb69ef2902033172eb8e1f24bbf2.thumbs%2F%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E5%81%B7%E8%A5%B2_000005.jpg&h=216f6740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事實: 阻唔到開會 改後幾日再開 你日日可以出?<br />\n要阻開會 點解唔直接揀幾個共派議員屋企去圍？<br />\n但你做唔做到?</span><br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩好好思考究竟我地點解要出黎<br />\n市民抗爭示威 係要比政府知道有幾激烈既反抗呀<br />\n實際對政府影響其實 分分鐘係 -0 hp,  我地就 -100hp<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">既然大家預左有人會被捕 如果有幾百人比人圍住捉 點解唔各區?</span></span><br />\n上年8月5 101 各區遊行開花影響性更大<br />\n方便大家轉場 &amp; 散水<br />\n街坊又易支援<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">過去一年入面有哂例子 大家知, 咩係有效, 咩係最蝕, 點解仲要揀最難?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070902105305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070902105305&h=b7a3ba40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"767bbd9805eb8f1e48754c708716229c069bd149","tid":2029911,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"政治宣傳層面上，畫面唔好睇不如唔好出<br />\n<br />\n俾啲創意"},{"pid":"a34ab57037dcc711cc892ae07c789e3c36956295","tid":2029911,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"諗清楚目標係乜先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>任何一個行動都要有清晰目標(<em>可達成而唔係異想天光</em>)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n五區嘅意義喺邊度？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阻到惡歌法？<br />\n諗清楚先好出嚟，唔好純粹為出而出，咁樣只會無成果送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，現階段圍攻立法會我都覺得做唔到<br />\n唔支持圍立法會，但都唔贊成分區行動<br />\n記住<br />\n行動要以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標為本</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">安全至上</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋依家打緊長期戰，要預咗短期內唔會有成果，所以唔好白白犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2307b772dab0dc83427127a07518683ee1ada890","tid":2029911,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"}]}